result.execSummary:
Luke Tyler Walton was extradited to another county, state or jurisdiction. Extradition means Luke Tyler Walton was accused or convicted of an offense in another county, state or jurisdiction and was taken there to face their charge(s) or conviction.

Notice to employers: It may be a violation of state law to discriminate against a job applicant because of an arrest or conviction record. Generally speaking, an employer may refuse to hire an applicant on the basis of a conviction only if the circumstances of the conviction substantially relate to the particular job. For more information, see Wisconsin Statute 111.335 and the Department of Workforce Development's publication, Arrest and Conviction Records under the Law.
result.caption: State of Wisconsin vs. Luke Tyler Walton

records.addlTxt: Per Dep. Henry, defendant was picked up 8/22/22 and extradited back to the State of Oklahoma.  Court removes 9/01/22 hearing from the calendar.

11:20 AM   Defendant Luke Tyler Walton appeared by video from the Door County Jall. Kevin Alfred Martin appeared by video for Luke Tyler Walton.   Attorney Nicholas Paul Grode in court for State of Wisconsin.  Atty Martin requests breakout room with defendant.  Back in session.   Court reviews fugitive complaint with defendant. State indicates they will not be issuing criminal charges regarding the possession of THC and drug paraphernalia charges, only here on the extradition matter.  Atty Martin advises defendant is the person that the State of Oklahoma is looking for.  Defendant wishes to be brought up to the courtroom to continue the hearing.  Defendant now present in court.  Court reviews waiver with defendant, finds defendant is waiving extradition and will voluntarily return, with law enforcement, back to the State of Oklahoma.  Defendant/Court sign waiver of extradition. Atty Martin request a review date be set to check status of whether defendant has been picked up yet or not.  Court sets review date for 9/01/22 at 8:00 am.
Attachments for Fugitive Complaint Walton, Luke Tyler
